name: You can't sit with us - spike neck & rainbow
description:
If you love Mean Girls then you need this in your life..
If you don't love Mean Girls.. Whyyyy??

This is a medium tee with rainbow tiedye and silver spike stud neck, one of my absolute fave tees of 2013! :)

If you order by Dec 8th this will be with you in time for Christmas - perfect present or treat for yourself..

On Wednesdays.. We wear pink.

name: Adidas dipdye vest - size large
description:
One for the boys and girls! (Buy for him.. Keep for yourself?! ;) )

If you want studs or crystals adding just send a message with your payment, it's no extra charge!

Xxx

name: Vintage Nike tee with silver stud swoosh
description:
This is a one off tee as its a vintage Nike tennis shirt that I stumbled across... Tiedyed with the gorgeous pastel colours and finished with a silver spiked swoosh... I love it!

This is a mens size medium and is a slightly softer looser fabric so will be good for sizes 8-12 depending on how you want it to fit..

If you want it cutting as a vest, no probs, just send me a message across with your order :)
Xxx

name: Party Clutch!
description:
Well, I thought a little Christmas line was needed for Cordelia & I realised that I didn't have the perfect clutch to go with my Xmas & new year dresses.. So what I couldn't find.. I created! 
Hope you love it as much as I do..

She is available in black, gold, silver and pink and each one will come with a slightly different pattern so that we all have something a little different :)

Please note that the silver does come slightly smaller than the other 3 (by 3cm)

At the moment I only have 2 of each colour available!

Lotsa love and merry Christmas! X

name: Wasted tee! - in whatever colour you would like!
description:
This tee looks ace on its own, tiedyed, dipdyed, cut as a vest, covered in studs... Whatever way you would like it!

Just let me know with your order how you would like it customising and I can do it for no extra charge for you..

This is a mens medium - but let me know if you need another size.

Lotsa love x

name: Vintage Nike hoody
description:
Nike hoody with Grey & pink dipdye effect, with silver spike studs around the nike logo on front which is in a green felt.

This says size small in the label and fits my size 10 mannequin snug so I would say it is more of a size 6-8uk.

This is a one off and a vintage item so please expect wear as you would from a vintage item - not a customised new item.

Lotsa love x

description:
What screams Christmas party more than a sparkly gold dress??
If you're a size 12 then this beauty needs to be yours..!

I only ever made the one, with black appliqu√© front and gold studded shoulders, be sure not to show up to the ball in the same dress as somebody else! Winner! :)

name: Panthera
description:
I've put two available... But that could very quickly change to one as I've already created 3 outfits in my head using this beauty!

description:
Eek.. Probably my favourite print out of all of them (till next week!) 
The colours are so beautiful and neutral with nudes and pinks, a hint of mint green within the red roses.. And then boom.. Two stunningly printed skeletons! Love it!

There's only two of these available.
Perfect Christmas present!

Hope you love it :)

name: Tiedye babygrow
description:
Pictures don't actually get any cuter than this!!!

Bring your baby into the world as a fashion icon with a Cordelia tiedye babygrow... All sized 0-3months.

X

name: Nike multi tie dye tee -as seen on HighHeelSuicide :)
description:
I'm sure you will have all seen the moment HighHeelSuicide posted this on her blog &reaching over 5000 likes! (Because I got VERY excited & shared it EVERYWHERE!haha)

Well, now it can be yours too! :)

One of my all time faves this is a men's size medium & will fit sizes 8-14 depending on how you want it to fit!

If you want it cut into a vest like the one features on LA then just let me know with your payment & also the same if you want studs adding - no extra charge for either :) xxx

name: Triangles are so hipster dipdye tee
description:
Triangles are so hipster!

Loving this tongue in cheek dipdye tee - covering the word 'triangle', 'hipster' and including studs - what more could one ask for? It's just like sooo hipsterism.

Yeh, I don't know what I'm on about either to be honest - either way, you need this in your wardrobe - with thick-rimmed glasses, witty banter, and a book you can only just read the title of. 

This is a men's medium (perfect for sizing 8-12) and I only have one available so first come first served on this beaut.. as always, let me know if you want it as a vest etc instead :)

name: Nirvana tiedye tee (or vest)
description:
Aw I might be biased but I'm loving the new colours in this months range - still got the beautiful pastel elements to them but with a little bit more kick! Especially with the new 'Flamingo Pink' & 'Bahama Blue'
...and what says 90s better than Nirvana!

This tee looks fab as a vest too - like the gorgeous Cara Delevingne has gone for - just pop me a message across with your payment if you want it like that, or studs adding, for no extra charge.. I have it available in a men's medium and a men's x.large so is great for most sizes.. Maybe try your boyfs/dads/uncles/neighbours on to see what would fit you best <3

****Please note that your top will not look exactly the same as the one pictured as all tops are tiedyed unique.. However I will try to get it as similar as poss and use the same colours***

name: I heart London
description:
I really do love London, if you do to, what better way to express it than on your chest! :)

This classic tourist tee has took a major twist with its pastel tiedye and studded heart

Can be cut into a test if preferred, just pop me a message across with your order and ill customise to how you like for no extra charge..

Lotsa love x
